      "doc_id": "02_expense_reimbursement_2022_deprecated.md",
      "reason": "Explicitly deprecated and superseded by 01_expense_reimbursement_2025.md. Clause 1 states it is retained only as a historical reference (仅作为制度沿革留档). Clause 4 states its approval thresholds have been replaced and must not be used as current authority. Clause 14 of the 2025 policy explicitly repeals the 2022 version (原《XX证券费用报销管理办法(2022版)》同时废止), effective 2025-01-01. The 2022 legacy thresholds (¥8,000→部门总经理, ¥30,000→分管副总) are fully replaced by AR-01 through AR-05 in 03_authorization_management.md Annex 2."
    }
  ],
